'''Mor Glayyd''' was the title of the leader of [[House Glayyd]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Ammuud/Legends|Ammuud]]. [[Ewwen Glayyd|Ewwen]] was the Mor Glayyd when [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] came to Ammuud.

